RowData.Text: How to fold origami candy boxes
How about folding origami candy box? Thus candy boxes can be had, which can be also as a home
decoration. Shall we get down to folding?
Materials acquired to fold
origami candy boxes
Origami paper
Scissors
How to fold origami candy
boxes？
Have you ever annoyed that you don’t have candy boxes to pack the candies? Candies are easily
melting in hot temperature. So it is not suitable to place them in the cabinet dispersedly. Maybe
origami candy box can help.
Step 1: fold a pentacle shape
Fold the square paper to a pentacle shape.
Note at the seventh step, a piece of scissors is
needed to cut the extra part.
Step 2: the ending work
Go on folding. Fold the upper five
angles.
Then origami candy box is formed. Don’t you think candy boxes are practical and wonderful? Have
a try. And make a house to the candies.
